<br>

- 🔬 Researching **synthetic CT & lung-mask generation** (GANs, diffusion) at INESC-TEC, part of the PHASE-IV AI EU project
- 🤖 Building **multi-agent LLM systems & MLOps pipelines** at Gresnovo
- 📄 3 papers in medical imaging & neural nets — 2 accepted, 1 under review
- 🌱 Big on the idea that consistent effort beats raw talent — independent study is a daily habit, not a phase
- ⚡ Fun fact: I once built a CNN from scratch in raw NumPy just to see if Bessel functions make better activations than ReLU (they're... interesting)

